# TSan suppressions for test_graph_tracker_race.
#
# This file starts empty. Run the test once with TSAN_OPTIONS pointing at
# this file, then add a `race:<symbol-substring>` line for every report
# whose stack does NOT touch tt::tt_metal::GraphTracker::processors. The
# remaining reports are the actual race we are proving.
#
# Format:
#   race:substring-of-function-name
# See https://github.com/google/sanitizers/wiki/threadsanitizerflags
